node.text: Meet Miraphora Mina & Eduardo Lima - together they are @MinaLimaDesign and they are the graphic designers on all the Harry Potter and Fantastic Beast films! They've designed everything from the Hogwarts Acceptance Letter to the Marauder's Map and The Daily Prophet. We chat with them about the letter, set experiences and more. Plus, they'll show you the completely custom Hogwarts Acceptance Letter YOU can win through our weekly House Celebration Instagram Giveaways!

node.title: Conversations with MinaLima: Wizarding World Graphic Designers
